Name: Pingball Ultra
About the game: Pingball Ultra is an online multiplayer action game based on popular timeless classic: Pong. Defeat your opponent by force or use strategic debuffs to flip their controls, make them smaller or blind them. Game is very simple, no learning curve. Play versus random players or challenge your friends.
